snippet.title: v0.1.2 New Girl Teaser
snippet.description:
Edgy teaser video for an H-game uwu

I wanted to make something different! I'm practicing animations and trying to make something really cool for the game. As I promised, Hero's Harem Guild will have a new girl every update, so making teasers for every one of them will be funny! I think...
